2. THE NATURE OF THE TRANSGRESSIVE IDENTITIES OF THE TV DRAMAS.

A prime example of a Telenovela-type passing through disruptive identities is, for example, the Spanish-language novel, which, although bordering the Italian style, can be assimilated to the Brazilian one.
